Class ShellUtils.CommandResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iritech.mqel704.ShellUtils.CommandResult
  • Enclosing class:
    ShellUtils

    public static class ShellUtils.CommandResult
extends java.lang.Object
    This class describes result of command.
    • result means result of command, 0 means normal, else means error, same to execute in linux shell.
    • successMsg means success message of command result.
    • errorMsg means error message of command result.
